name: Lucky Races Original Racer Mint Keys (Ethereum)

metadata.description: Lucky Races Original Racer Mint Key, redeemable for up to a year. Once redeemed you will be put in the queue to have your racer minted with the next batch. When your Racer is minted, we burn your key and send you a brand new Original Racer ERC-721 NFT on Ethereum. If left unredeemed longer than 1 year, your key will automatically get redeemed and you will receive your Original Racer on Ethereum with the final batch. License at  https://www.luckyraces.com/original-racer-license
metadata.name: Lucky Races Original Racer Mint Key
